{"_path":"/guides/motorcycle-permit-vs-license","_dir":"guides","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"Motorcycle Permit vs License: How to Get Your Permit","description":"Motorcycle permit vs license explained, plus how to get a motorcycle permit step by step, the restrictions that apply, and how to upgrade to a full endorsement.","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h1","props":{"id":"motorcycle-permit-vs-license"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Motorcycle Permit vs License"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"A motorcycle permit and a motorcycle license are two stages of the same journey. The permit lets you learn to ride under restrictions, and the license (or endorsement) lets you ride freely. Understanding the difference helps you plan the fastest path to riding legally."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"the-difference-at-a-glance"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"The Difference at a Glance"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"table","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"thead","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"tr","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"th","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"th","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Motorcycle Permit"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"th","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Motorcycle License / Endorsement"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"tbody","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"tr","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"How you get it"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Pass a written knowledge test"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Pass or waive the skills test"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"tr","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Restrictions"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"No passengers, no night riding, no highways (typical)"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"None specific to motorcycles"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"tr","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Purpose"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Learning to ride and practicing"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Riding freely on public roads"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"tr","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Validity"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Temporary (months)"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Standard license term"}]}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Exact restrictions vary by state, so confirm with your licensing agency. Our "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"/guides/motorcycle-license-requirements-by-state"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"requirements by state"}]},{"type":"text","value":" hub links to each program."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"how-to-get-a-motorcycle-permit"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"How to Get a Motorcycle Permit"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"step-1-meet-the-minimum-age"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Step 1: Meet the Minimum Age"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Each state sets a minimum age for a motorcycle permit. Younger applicants may face extra requirements, such as a mandatory rider course or parental consent."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"step-2-study-the-motorcycle-handbook"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Step 2: Study the Motorcycle Handbook"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Your state publishes a motorcycle operator manual covering road signs, traffic laws, and safe riding strategies. This is the source material for the knowledge test."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"step-3-pass-the-written-knowledge-test"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Step 3: Pass the Written Knowledge Test"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Visit your DMV (or take it online where offered), present identification, pay the fee, and pass the written exam to receive your permit."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"step-4-ride-within-the-restrictions"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Step 4: Ride Within the Restrictions"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"With a permit you can practice on public roads within the posted limits, no passengers, daylight only, and no highways in most states, while you prepare for the skills test."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"from-permit-to-license"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"From Permit to License"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Once you have a permit and some practice, you complete the licensing process by passing the skills test, or by completing an approved rider course that waives it. The full process is covered in our "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"/guides/how-to-get-a-motorcycle-license"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"step-by-step licensing guide"}]},{"type":"text","value":"."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"courses-that-help-you-upgrade"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Courses That Help You Upgrade"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"_1-motorcycle-safety-foundation"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"1. Motorcycle Safety Foundation"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Its Basic RiderCourse builds the exact skills the road test evaluates and provides a path to licensing."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"/dir/motorcycle_safety_foundation"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Learn more about Motorcycle Safety Foundation"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"hr","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"_2-motorcycle-safety-school"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"2. Motorcycle Safety School"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Offers the Basic RiderCourse and BRC2 license-waiver course to take you from permit to endorsement."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"/dir/motorcycle_safety_school"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Learn more about Motorcycle Safety School"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"hr","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"_3-motorcycle-training-academy"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"3. Motorcycle Training Academy"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Provides MSF-curriculum novice courses plus advanced and three-wheel training."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"/dir/motorcycle_training_academy"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Learn more about Motorcycle Training Academy"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"hr","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"frequently-asked-questions"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Frequently Asked Questions"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"how-do-i-get-a-motorcycle-permit"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"How do I get a motorcycle permit?"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Meet your state's minimum age, study the motorcycle handbook, then pass the written knowledge test at the DMV. You will receive a permit with riding restrictions."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"can-i-ride-with-just-a-motorcycle-permit"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Can I ride with just a motorcycle permit?"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Yes, but only within the restrictions, typically no passengers, no nighttime riding, and no highway use. The permit is meant for supervised practice and learning."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"how-long-is-a-motorcycle-permit-valid"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"How long is a motorcycle permit valid?"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Permit validity varies by state, often several months to a year, and some states limit how many times you can renew it. Check your state's rules."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"do-i-need-a-permit-before-a-rider-course"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Do I need a permit before a rider course?"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Some courses require a permit first, others accept complete beginners. Confirm the requirement with the provider when you register."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"hr","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"em","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Next step: "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"/guides/how-to-get-a-motorcycle-license"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"how to get a motorcycle license"}]},{"type":"text","value":"."}]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"the-difference-at-a-glance","depth":2,"text":"The Difference at a Glance"},{"id":"how-to-get-a-motorcycle-permit","depth":2,"text":"How to Get a Motorcycle Permit","children":[{"id":"step-1-meet-the-minimum-age","depth":3,"text":"Step 1: Meet the Minimum 